text: Aranka Hennyei (1900 - 1987) was a Hungarian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1900 births Category:1987 deaths Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
